    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Sara Mosle's article about the powerlessness of volunteering to effect change touched a nerve with readers. Most were certain she had made a difference; others were horrified at her conclusions. Many readers thought Jeffrey Goldberg's report on the Haqqania madrasa inflamed prejudices.</p>
